This paper involves the use of deep learning for image processing and analysis, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also involves the use of neural networks, which falls under artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of deep learning for image processing also falls under machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves the use of neural networks for image processing, which falls under neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the paper involves the use of microscopy images, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM).
